** Dinobot was just about to target another enemy when there was a sudden 
voice over his communicator, the sounds of the famanin voice obviously 
belonging to that which was their, so called, commander.
He growled and shifted his weight at the order to cease the battle and 
gather at her location, thinking that he had not even gotten right into the 
battle before it already seemed to be powering down. However, from 
Scattershot's earlier attack he had obtained a slight amount of damage just 
below his left shoulder-plate. Which ment that he had fought.
However, there seemed to have been reported a life at stake, so he had no 
choice other then that to cease his actions and go to the commander's call. 
Though, he did not have to like it!
Dinobot growled and scanned the battlefield, not only for the commander's 
location but for Tavatron's as well. Surely she had recieved the same 
transmission and might be on her way. But if she was trying to defeat an 
enemy, he might be of assistance to her...as he always was before.**
